WEBVTT

00:00:58.825 --> 00:01:02.380
I never practiced law a day in my life;

00:01:02.404 --> 00:01:04.388
I pretty much wasn't allowed to.

00:01:04.412 --> 00:01:06.009
(Laughter)

00:01:07.150 --> 00:01:10.631
But today, against my better judgment,

00:01:10.655 --> 00:01:12.976
against the advice of my own wife,

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:16.976
I want to try to dust off
some of those legal skills --

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:19.359
what's left of those legal skills.

00:01:19.383 --> 00:01:21.129
I don't want to tell you a story.

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:24.364
I want to make a case.

00:01:24.388 --> 00:01:26.754
I want to make a hard-headed,

00:01:26.778 --> 00:01:27.976
evidence-based,

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:31.174
dare I say lawyerly case,